          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>First-order unification, following McBride's
<fr:link href="/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/mcbrideFirstorderUnification2003/" title="First-order unification by structural recursion" uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/mcbrideFirstorderUnification2003/" display-uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/mcbrideFirstorderUnification2003/" type="local">structurally recursive unification algorithm</fr:link>.
The algorithm is built using
<fr:link href="/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FS/" title="Löb induction on families" uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FS/" display-uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FS/" type="local">Löb induction on families</fr:link> over the
<fr:link href="/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/sss-00G8/" title="The category of thinnings" uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00G8/" display-uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00G8/" type="local">category of thinnings</fr:link> with the well-founded measure given
by size of the scope.</html:p>
